HELP XT_NEW_PUSH_BUTTON_F                               Steve Knight, Oct 93
                                                        SIREN Project

    xt_new_push_button_f(
        PARENT, [NAME], BINDING1, ..., BINDINGn, [MANAGED],
        STRING, ITEM_LIST
    ) -> WIDGET

This procedure creates a Motif push button widget.  The topmost arguments are
used to prepare the XmNlabelString resource via *SPRINTF and obey the
(moderately complex) argument rules for -sprintf-.  The remaining arguments
are processed using *XT_NEW_ARGS.

See also:
    HELP *SPRINTF
    HELP *PRINTF
    HELP *XT_NEW_ARGS
